        public static VDiskAPI.Entry parseXVDiskMetadata(HttpResponse response)
        Parses the JSON in the the 'x-VDisk-metadata' header field of the http response.
        参数:
        response - The http response for the downloaded file.
        返回:
        An Entry object based on the metadata JSON. Can be null if metadata isn't available.

      • parseFileSize

        private static long parseFileSize(HttpResponse response,
                 VDiskAPI.Entry metadata)
        Determines the size of the downloaded file.
        参数:
        response - The http response for the file whose size we're interested in.
        metadata - The metadata associated with the file. Can be null if unavailable.
        返回:
        The determined file size. -1 if the size of the file can't be determined.
